<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich III. Schenk von Limpurg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Andreas Haller und Jakob Topler, Bürger zu Nürnberg, an und bittet in ihrem Streit mit Götz von Berlichingen und Hans von Eichelheim um raschen Austrag.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_73" id="36r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_73_r1l2"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Schenken <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l3">cʒu <expan>lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / vnd hauptman deʒ <expan>lantfr<ex>ids</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_73_r1l4">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als Andres haller vnd Jacob Topler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l5"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu euch <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> von etvvaʒ ſache wegen / als ſie mit <expan>Göcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l6">von <expan>Perlıchinge<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd hanſen von Eẏchelſheim 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu hanſen </del> cʒu handeln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l7"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> der </del> als ſie euch das ſelber auch wol <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> werden / <expan>Hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l8">vns <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger geſagt / vvie Jr euch <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l9"><expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jn bederſeit . cʒurichten <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>fange<ex>n</ex></expan> habt <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l10">die <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> ~ 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> b </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> darẏnne durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>günſtikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l12">laſſet <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Alſo daʒ </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_73_r1l11">vnd </ab></add> Jn der ſache ein kurcʒ ende vnd auſʒtrag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l13">machet / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ~ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_73" id="36r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Schenken, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        czu <expan>Lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und hauptman dez
                                <expan>lantfr<ex>ids</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als Andres Haller und Jacob Topler,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger,
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu euch <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        von etwaz sache wegen, als sie mit <expan>Göcze<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Perlichinge<ex>n</ex></expan> und Hansen von Eychelsheim czu
                        handeln <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als sie euch das selber auch wol
                                <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> werden,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger gesagt, wie ir euch
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache
                            <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in bederseit czurichten
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>fange<ex>n</ex></expan> habt.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ew die
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, darynne durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>günstikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> lasset
                            <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein <add>und</add> in der sache ein
                        kurcz ende und ausztrag machet, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
